ointed that Cardiff University, as a member of Universities Wales, has not openly discussed their views on the Welsh baccalaureate with the committee. This reluctance to engage in the conversation could be seen as uncooperative and might contribute to the perception that there is something to hide regarding the universities' stance on the Welsh baccalaureate.">
