 has reached out to universities directly to determine their views and has found consistent support for the value of the Welsh baccalaureate, with no indication that it disadvantages Welsh students.&#10;4. Qualifications Wales has an individual whose role is to ensure that universities across the United Kingdom understand the value of Welsh qualifications, including the Welsh baccalaureate. This will become increasingly important as English and Welsh qualifications diverge.">
